		<div id="question_9">
			<div id="question">
				<p>You play a game with a friend where you flip a coin. If you get heads you win, if not then it is your friends turn. Is it better to go first or second in this game?</p>
			</div>


			<div id="display_answer">
				<input type="button" name="answer" value="Answer" onclick="show_ans_9()" />

				<div id="answer_9"  style="display:none;" class="answer_list" > 
					<p>It is better to go first. The first player has a 50/50 chance of winning where as the second player needs the first person to get tails (0.5 chance) and then must get heads (0.5 chance) which has a probability of 0.25.</p>
				</div>
